TYPE LOCALITY. Not mentioned in the original description; given as Sistan, 
<collectingCountry id="F37D7674FFAEFF9BFC274DDE5260FCBF" box="[1003,1048,764,787]" name="Iran" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">Iran</collectingCountry>
